WEBVTT

00:00:01.012 --> 00:00:07.660
Good evening, everybody. Thank you for joining us again tonight. I have my sweetheart with me tonight.

00:00:07.661 --> 00:00:19.951
I told her we will go ahead and pray and seek the Lord to see what He has for us tonight concerning our nation.

00:00:19.953 --> 00:00:35.572
Today, when I was driving around and doing errands, I saw in the spirit a headline in the New York Times.

00:00:35.573 --> 00:00:53.679
The caption in bold letters said, 'Terror in Manhattan.'Thank you, son.

00:00:53.680 --> 00:01:04.471
'Terror in Manhattan.'In the picture, I saw a lot of smoke and a building.

00:01:04.472 --> 00:01:32.152
I saw 'Terror in Manhattan'in bold on the front of this newspaper, and below it, 'Terror strikes again in America.'Then it had the article of what happened.

00:01:32.153 --> 00:01:47.369
As I was praying—I guess we're just going to jump right into this to save you time—I saw an umbrella with beautiful colors; it was a protection.

00:01:47.370 --> 00:02:06.083
But because of choices that were made, this umbrella had holes all in it.

00:02:06.084 --> 00:02:14.839
Decisions being made over the years caused the holes to get bigger and bigger.

00:02:14.840 --> 00:02:28.130
The more the umbrella was covering over America, the more people were holding it and were excited to have it because it blocked the storms and the plan of the enemy.

00:02:28.131 --> 00:02:40.697
This umbrella was a covering. As American citizens or people around the world, you have this prayer covering from the churches.

00:02:40.698 --> 00:02:56.314
But as you make decisions against God's word, against God's plan, and against what God originally wanted for us, you cause holes in your umbrella.

00:02:56.315 --> 00:03:05.307
We repent, and the covering is still there, but there were holes in it because of those decisions.

00:03:05.308 --> 00:03:29.037
I saw these holes that were seemingly really small at the beginning, like pinholes, but over the course of time, the holes got larger and larger until the umbrella was no longer there.

00:03:29.038 --> 00:03:43.056
The Lord showed me the prayer covering of a home and the importance of the male being the head of the household.

00:03:43.057 --> 00:03:53.156
The man brings a covering over it, and the wife provides a prayer covering, too. There is so much importance in a man leading his family.

00:03:53.157 --> 00:04:08.380
The Lord was showing me the importance of righteous men in the household rising up and being what God has called you to be: lead your family, take them to church, pray with your kids, and pray with your wife.

00:04:08.381 --> 00:04:14.914
Be a godly spouse. Speak good things over your children and your wife.

00:04:14.915 --> 00:04:25.645
Bless your children and your wife spiritually, physically, and financially. Whatever you can do, you be that head.

00:04:25.646 --> 00:04:56.265
I saw that as America goes, as the church goes, and as big decisions go, that covering—no matter how much we prayed and asked God to cover things—the more unbiblical decisions were made, like those made in New York by the mayor, the more it caused holes.

00:04:56.266 --> 00:05:04.413
I saw a terror attack, and the Lord said, 'Do you see the power of prayer, Brandon? What it does? It brings that covering.

00:05:04.414 --> 00:05:27.882
But because you make unrighteous decisions, you open the door for the enemy.'I said, 'Lord, I need scriptures.'He brought up Job and other scriptures that Diana wrote down.

00:05:27.883 --> 00:05:42.968
The devil said, 'You've put a hedge around Job and I'm not able to touch it,'but if you remove that hedge, what Job feared the most came on him.

00:05:42.969 --> 00:05:50.077
He opened the door through fear; fear tolerated, faith contaminated.

00:05:50.078 --> 00:06:02.260
As he was making sacrifices out of fear for his children and acting out of fear, he opened the door for it.

00:06:02.261 --> 00:06:13.416
Now, when we have a church covering and you keep praying over it, He showed me the thorns.

00:06:13.417 --> 00:06:23.617
Not Hosea, I believe it was in Ezekiel—whoever breaks a hedge, the serpent will bite him.

00:06:23.618 --> 00:06:49.914
Okay, that's Ecclesiastes 10:8: 'Whoever breaks a hedge, a serpent will bite him.'As you break the hedge and that umbrella of covering, it allows the enemy to come in and kill, steal, and destroy.

00:06:49.915 --> 00:07:20.600
We have authority, but if you keep making ungodly decisions, and He says, 'I want you to live righteously,'but you are sleeping around while claiming to be a praying Christian, you are opening the door.

00:07:20.601 --> 00:07:27.058
That covering gets holes in it because you are allowing sin in.

00:07:27.059 --> 00:07:39.780
That is what the Lord was showing me today: the covering of prayer over America as we keep making these bad decisions.

00:07:39.781 --> 00:07:46.795
That's what He keeps talking about in 1 Corinthians 5:5. It is not His will for any of us to perish.

00:07:46.796 --> 00:07:53.679
Ladies and gentlemen, you think because you go through a hard time for a season, that is God's judgment.

00:07:53.680 --> 00:08:09.024
True judgment is separation from God for eternity. It's not the day-to-day hard times.

00:08:09.025 --> 00:08:12.784
The way the Lord kept showing me was, 'That is not judgment, Brandon.

00:08:12.785 --> 00:08:18.294
True judgment is whenever you are going to hell forever and there is no returning.

00:08:18.295 --> 00:08:39.359
It's the point where there is no turning back; you are in hell forever.'The moment you take your last breath and you do not have Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior, if you are not a born-again Christian, that is true judgment.

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:48.246
But having a shaking to awaken people—like what I have seen coming—they will all say, 'This is judgment.

00:08:48.247 --> 00:09:00.274
God's mad,'and they will call it an Ichabod. 'God has departed from America.'No, it is people making poor choices and voting unwisely.

00:09:00.275 --> 00:09:10.486
They keep thinking they can do these things without repercussions. I am trying to tell you what I keep seeing.

00:09:10.487 --> 00:09:22.958
When I saw the headlines in the paper, I said, 'Oh Lord.'He said, 'Brandon, do you see the importance of a choice?

00:09:22.959 --> 00:09:37.283
Do you see the importance of the prayer covering that you bring over your family?'That covers you; you have the authority to pray that your family is always in the right place at the right time.

00:09:37.284 --> 00:09:47.843
But I am talking about as a city as a whole. You keep making poor choices and voting in ways that allow the enemy to get a stronghold in an area.

00:09:47.844 --> 00:09:55.827
That is why I was praying over these things today. People might say, 'Brandon, you're being too harsh,'but I am just telling you what I am praying over today.

00:09:55.827 --> 00:10:07.278
It is a little raw, but this is what I am seeing in the headlines. I saw a great shaking coming again.

00:10:07.279 --> 00:10:14.104
I keep seeing these things, and quite frankly, it is very sobering.

